<div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto p-3 md:p-8 bg-white" data-controller="exercise-checker">

  <%= render 'shared/page_header', pagina: @pagina %>

  <!-- Info Box -->
  <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 p-4 md:p-6 pb-8 rounded-lg">
    <p class="text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4 font-semibold">
      <span class="text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500">•</span> I <strong>verbi irregolari</strong> non seguono lo schema della coniugazione a cui appartengono. Possono variare:
    </p>

    <ul class="space-y-3 text-base md:text-lg text-gray-700">
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>nella radice</strong> → il verbo <em>andare</em> al presente è <strong>vado</strong> (e non <del>ando</del>);</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-green-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>nella desinenza</strong> → il verbo <em>venire</em> al presente è <strong>vengo</strong> (e non <del>venio</del>);</span>
      </li>
      <li class="flex items-start gap-2">
        <span class="text-orange-600 font-bold">•</span>
        <span><strong>in entrambe</strong> → il verbo <em>dire</em> al passato remoto è <strong>dissi</strong>.</span>
      </li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 1: IMPARARE TUTTI -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">1</span>
      Collega ciascuna voce verbale all'infinito corrispondente.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
      <!-- Voci verbali -->
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-4">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-700 mb-3">Voci verbali</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2">feci</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2">ho scritto</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2">dico</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2">lessi</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2">caddi</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2">ho aperto</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2">posso</div>
          <div class="bg-blue-50 rounded px-3 py-2">vado</div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Infiniti -->
      <div class="bg-white rounded-lg p-4 border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200">
        <h3 class="font-bold text-green-700 mb-3">Infiniti</h3>
        <div class="space-y-2 text-base md:text-lg">
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2">dire → <em>dico</em></div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2">fare → <em>feci</em></div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2">scrivere → <em>ho scritto</em></div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2">aprire → <em>ho aperto</em></div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2">potere → <em>posso</em></div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2">leggere → <em>lessi</em></div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2">andare → <em>vado</em></div>
          <div class="bg-green-50 rounded px-3 py-2">cadere → <em>caddi</em></div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 2: Complete table -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8" data-controller="fill-blanks">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">2</span>
      Completa la tabella e indica con una X se il verbo è o non è irregolare.
    </h2>

    <div class="overflow-x-auto">
      <table class="w-full border-collapse text-sm md:text-base">
        <thead>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-100">
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Verbo</th>
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Presente</th>
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Passato prossimo</th>
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Passato remoto</th>
            <th class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-300 px-4 py-3 font-bold">Irregolare?</th>
          </tr>
        </thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold">camminare</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="cammino" data-correct-answer="cammino">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="ho camminato" data-correct-answer="ho camminato">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="camminai" data-correct-answer="camminai">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center">
                <label><input type="radio" name="irr1" value="si"> Sì</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="irr1" value="no"> No</label>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold">volere</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="voglio" data-correct-answer="voglio">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="ho voluto" data-correct-answer="ho voluto">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="volli" data-correct-answer="volli">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center">
                <label><input type="radio" name="irr2" value="si"> Sì</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="irr2" value="no"> No</label>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-white">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold">stare</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="sto" data-correct-answer="sto">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="sono stato" data-correct-answer="sono stato">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="stetti" data-correct-answer="stetti">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center">
                <label><input type="radio" name="irr3" value="si"> Sì</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="irr3" value="no"> No</label>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
          <tr class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50">
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3 font-semibold">tornare</td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="torno" data-correct-answer="torno">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="sono tornato" data-correct-answer="sono tornato">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <input type="text" class="w-full border-b-2 border-dotted border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 bg-white text-right px-2 focus:outline-none" data-fill-blanks-target="input" data-answer="tornai" data-correct-answer="tornai">
            </td>
            <td class="border border-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-200 px-4 py-3">
              <div class="flex gap-2 justify-center">
                <label><input type="radio" name="irr4" value="si"> Sì</label>
                <label><input type="radio" name="irr4" value="no"> No</label>
              </div>
            </td>
          </tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>
    </div>
  </div>

  <!-- Exercise 3 -->
  <div class="bg-white p-4 md:p-6 pb-8">
    <h2 class="text-lg md:text-xl font-bold mb-4 flex items-center gap-2">
      <span class="flex-shrink-0 bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-500 text-white rounded-full w-8 h-8 md:w-10 md:h-10 inline-flex items-center justify-center">3</span>
      Coniuga questi verbi al passato remoto e scrivi sul quaderno una frase con ciascuno.
    </h2>

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-4 text-base md:text-lg">
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        leggere
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        ridere
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        crescere
      </div>
      <div class="bg-<%= @pagina.base_color %>-50 rounded-lg p-3 text-center font-semibold text-gray-700">
        mettere
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="text-right text-sm text-gray-500 mb-6">
    Esercizi p. <%= link_to "175", pagina_path("nvl5_gram_p175"), class: "text-gray-600 hover:text-gray-800 underline" %>
  </div>

  <%= render 'shared/exercise_controls' %>
</div>
